The universe began with The Boundless Pattern, an infinite weave through which all planes are born through sound.

[signal arg="bg:stars"]
Senialis found her way into the plane we know and eventually made the ultimate sacrifice to stop an encroaching threat, becoming the planet we know today.

[signal arg="bg:world"]
Another Senialis, a bard, was named after her and he has the ego to match. We'll see how that plays out for him, chief.

